<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            text-align: center;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    <p>You have requested to reset your password for your account associated with the email {{ user.getAdresseemail() }}. Please use the following code to proceed with resetting your password. This code is valid for only 30 minutes:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px;">
        <span style="font-size: 24px; color: #0056b3;">{{ reset_code }}</span>
    </div>

    <a href="your-website-url-to-reset-password?code={{ reset_code }}" class="button">Reset Password</a>

    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have any concerns.</p>

    <p class="footer">Thank you,<br>Your Website Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
